  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Indigenous Ecuadorians in the Amazon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Friends of Ikiam works with indigenous people, living in the Amazon rainforest, to identify current and future challenges that they face. Our goal is to help these communities meet their challenges successfully. We assist with planning and implementing projects that allow indigenous people to keep their culture intact and reduce the impact of  population growth and other external factors  on the rainforest. We are currently working on water, sanitation, agriculture, and conservation projects.</narrative>
  </description>
